Eric Blore https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eric_Blore 0 Eric Blore (23 December 1887 – 2 March 1959) was an English comic actor who worked in the United States beginning in the 1920s and had a very busy career in Hollywood films in the 1930 and 1940s. Blore was born in Finchley, Middlesex, England.
